<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>My API</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      a {
        color: #333;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Welcome to My API</h1>
    <p>
      This is a simple API that I created to learn how to create APIs. It is
      build with <%= locals.stack || "Node.js"%>.
    </p>
    <p>
      This API allows you to manage flashcards. You can create, read, update,
      and delete flashcards.
    </p>
    <h2>Endpoints:</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="/api/flashcards">View all flashcards</a></li>
      <li><a href="/api/flashcards/:id">View a specific flashcard</a></li>
      <li><a href="/api/flashcards/create">Create a new flashcard</a></li>
      <li><a href="/api/flashcards/update/:id">Update a flashcard</a></li>
      <li><a href="/api/flashcards/delete/:id">Delete a flashcard</a></li>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html>
